%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e5a3716080194819fc04c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221172%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYoung%20people%20are%20spending%20hundreds%20on%20social%20clubs%20and%20gym%20memberships%20to%20make%20friends.%20%3Cp%3EIvan%20Pantic%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20young%20worker%20complained%20about%20feeling%20lonely%20in%20a%20hotel%20room%20for%20a%20work%20trip%20and%20sparked%20an%20online%20debate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESocial%20media%20users%20are%20divided%20with%20some%20criticizing%20young%20people%20for%20not%20enjoying%20their%20own%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20is%20facing%20a%20loneliness%20epidemic%20as%20young%20people%20feel%20increasingly%20isolated%20in%20a%20digital%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20young%20worker%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20and%20sparked%20a%20debate%20about%20loneliness%20and%20the%20relative%20merits%20of%20solo%20business%20trips%20after%20posting%20a%20TikTok%20complaining%20about%20feeling%20bored%20and%20alone%20in%20a%20hotel%20room%20for%20a%20work%20trip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiley%20Scruggs%2C%20a%20senior%20creative%20strategist%20at%20Discover%20Financial%20Services%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20posted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40ri.scruggs%2Fvideo%2F7338246172261403950%3Fis_from_webapp%3D1%26sender_device%3Dpc%26web_id%3D7156168240485582341%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Evideo%20on%20TikTok%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20sitting%20around%20in%20a%20hotel%20room%20in%20suburban%20Illinois.%20The%20video%20showed%20clips%20of%20her%20lying%20on%20the%20bed%2C%20sitting%20on%20the%20window%2C%20and%20standing%20in%20the%20shower.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20text%20in%20the%20video%20says%3A%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20I%20hate%20being%20a%20corporate%20girlie%20because%20what%20am%20I%20supposed%20to%20do%20alone%20in%20a%20hotel%20in%20the%20Illinois%20suburbs%20on%20a%20Wednesday%20night%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%2C%20which%20has%20accumulated%20almost%20200%2C000%20views%20on%20TikTok%2C%20has%20been%20flooded%20with%20comments%20from%20people%20suggesting%20ideas%20on%20what%20Scruggs%20could%20do%20on%20her%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20order%20chilis%20and%20watch%20the%20office%20reruns%20that%20are%20always%20on%20hotel%20TVs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BTake%20a%20bath!!%20Drink%20some%20wine!!%20Find%20local%20restaurant%20to%20try!!%20I%20love%20playing%20Eloise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20has%20also%20gone%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcoldhealing%2Fstatus%2F1763961260679311855%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eviral%20on%20X%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20formerly%20Twitter%20%E2%80%94%20but%20users%20are%20divided%2C%20with%20some%20defending%20her%20and%20others%20criticizing%20young%20people%20for%20apparently%20being%20unable%20to%20enjoy%20their%20own%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanactualwalnut%2Fstatus%2F1764166187145924979%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DPMwdYzIW-KjlUoFRZMe6vg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EOne%20X%20user%20commented%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20post%20that%20has%20over%20six%20million%20views%3A%20%26quot%3BLiterally%200%20hate%20to%20this%20girl%20but%20y'all%20really%20need%20to%20learn%20the%20concept%20of%20enjoying%20your%20own%20company%20and%20also%20without%20having%20a%20list%20of%20little%20side%20quests%20to%20do.%20You%20realize%20how%20incredible%20it%20is%20to%20have%20an%20evening%20to%20yourself%20in%20a%20new%20place%20in%20a%20hotel%20you%20didn't%20pay%20for%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOrder%20room%20service%20and%20dance%20around%20and%20jump%20on%20the%20bed.%20I'm%20lowkey%20scared%20of%20people%20who%20can't%20fathom%20just%20doing%20nothing%20alone.%20That%20is%20my%20preferred%20weekend%20every%20weekend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20user%20agreed%3A%20%26quot%3BCorporate%20life%20takes%20so%20much%20of%20your%20time%20and%20energy%2C%20that%20you%20actually%20forget%20how%20to%20live%3B%20It's%20a%20machine%20that%20perpetually%20keeps%20you%20plugged%20in%2C%20even%20when%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20be%2C%20and%20this%20is%20what%20it%20does%20to%20people...%20They%20spend%20so%20much%20time%20making%20a%20living%20that%20they%20forget%20how%20to%20live.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20agreed%20with%20Scruggs%20saying%20there%20often%20aren't%20many%20fun%20things%20to%20do%20on%20a%20solo%20business%20trip%20in%20the%20suburbs%20and%20it's%20not%20wrong%20to%20desire%20company%20when%20you're%20feeling%20alone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20people%20said%20that%20business%20hotels%20often%20don't%20have%20%26quot%3Broom%20service%26quot%3B%20and%20are%20intended%20to%20be%20places%20to%20sleep%20and%20nothing%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoneliness%20has%20become%20a%20huge%20problem%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20the%20US%20Surgeon%20General%20Vivek%20Murthy%20declaring%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hhs.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fsurgeon-general-social-connection-advisory.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eloneliness%20epidemic%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023.%20Murthy%20said%20loneliness%20is%20linked%20to%20poor%20mental%20and%20physical%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20particularly%20affecting%20Gen%20Z.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20young%20professionals%20who%20joined%20the%20workplace%20after%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20were%20expected%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcure-for-gen-z-loneliness-heading-returning-to-office-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ework%20remotely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20felt%20extremely%20isolated%20and%20lonely%20as%20a%20result.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%20peo