2%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.assettype.com%2Fbloombergquint%252F2017-06%252F46c01b1a-0c85-493f-994b-b6009b70cbc6%252F301506555_1-47.jpg%3Frect%3D0%252C0%252C4000%252C2250%26auto%3Dformat%252Ccompress%26w%3D1200%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubbed%20India's%20Manchester%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtvprofit.com%2Fbusiness%2Fknitwear-exports-from-tirupur-to-clock-rs-30000-crore-in-fy20%5C%22%3Ethe%20southern%20town%20of%20Tiruppur%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fa%3E%20used%20to%20be%20a%20bustling%20hub%20of%20textiles%20barely%20four%20years%20ago.%20From%20the%20global%20financial%20crisis%20of%202008%20and%20the%20banning%20of%20dyeing%20units%20by%20the%20Madras%20High%20Court%20in%202011%20to%20demonetisation%20in%202016-the%20industry%20withstood%20blow%20after%20relentless%20blow%20and%20survived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcoronavirus-hit-textile-units-in-tamil-nadus-tiruppur-turns-to-mask-production-2209993%5C%22%3EThen%20came%20Covid-19%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20as%20the%20world%20shut%20down%20in%202020%2C%20so%20too%20did%20Tiruppur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20'Revenge%20Buying'%20Pushed%20Up%20Prices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%20and%20early%202022%2C%20as%20lockdowns%20were%20cautiously%20lifted%2C%20consumers%20across%20the%20world%20began%20to%20indulge%20in%20'revenge%20buying'.%20Having%20been%20deprived%20of%20a%20normal%20life%2C%20they%20splurged%20on%20garments.%20Cash%20registers%20were%20ringing%20in%20Tiruppur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20demand%20surged%2C%20prices%20of%20cotton%20skyrocketed%20by%2053%25%20in%202022%2C%20while%20prices%20of%20yarn%20doubled.%20Cotton%20growers%20and%20traders%20the%20world%20over%20cashed%20in%20on%20the%20opportunity.%20Traders%20and%20large%20corporates%20hoarded%20cotton%2C%20pushing%20the%20prices%20to%20unsustainable%20highs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20small%20and%20mid-sized%20mills%20and%20garment%20manufacturers%20in%20Tiruppur%20were%20unable%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20these%20prices%2C%20and%20so%2C%20their%20working%20capital%20took%20a%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EExports%20Dried%20Up%20Globally%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine%2C%20triggering%20economic%20sanctions%20being%20imposed%20by%20Europe%20and%20the%20US.%20Russia%20reacted%20by%20cutting%20off%20gas%20supply%20to%20Europe%2C%20thereby%20trebling%20energy%20costs.%20As%20prices%20of%20essential%20commodities%20soared%20in%20Europe%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20garments%20nosedived.%20Families%20stopped%20purchasing%20clothing%20seasonally%2C%20preferring%20to%20utilise%20their%20existing%20wardrobes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20market%20for%20Tiruppur's%20exporters%20dried%20up.%20Desperate%20to%20make%20a%20living%2C%20exporters%20then%20turned%20to%20the%20domestic%20garment%20market%20to%20sell%20their%20garments.%20This%20move%20added%20severe%20pressure%20to%20the%20already%20wafer-thin%20margins%2C%20as%20domestic%20garment%20manufacturers%20were%20now%20forced%20to%20compete%20with%20exporters%20who%20were%20vying%20for%20the%20same%20pie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20consumer%2C%20taking%20a%20cue%20from%20the%20global%20consumer%2C%20also%20cut%20back%20on%20spending%20on%20garments.%20The%20only%20solace%20is%20that%20the%20demand%20slowdown%20in%20India%20is%20not%20as%20bad%20as%20it%20is%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20whole%2C%20the%20industry%20has%20taken%20a%20severe%20hit.%20Today%2C%20Tiruppur's%20apparel%20makers%20are%20producing%20barely%2030%25%20of%20their%20capacity.%20There%20are%20no%20takers%20for%20their%20clothes.%20Fabric%20wholesalers%20are%20sitting%20on%20warehouses%20filled%20to%20the%20brim%20without%20any%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20peak%20sale%20seasons%20of%20Deepavali%2C%20Christmas%20and%20New%20Year%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Sankaranti%20and%20Pongal%20periods%20of%202024%2C%20have%20all%20been%20washouts.%20The%20future%20looks%20grim%20too%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20that%20has%20increased%20shipping%20costs%20globally%20due%20to%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELosing%20The%20Competitive%20Edge%20To%20Bangladesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%2C%20and%20one%20that%20has%20not%20been%20addressed%20satisfactorily%20thus%20far%2C%20is%20the%20import%20of%20cheap%20garments%20from%20Bangladesh%20and%20fabric%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%2050%25%20of%20all%20imports%20of%20textiles%20and%20apparel%20by%20India%20is%20from%20China%20(38%25)%20and%20Bangladesh%20(12%25)%2C%20as%20per%202022-23%20data%20on%20the%20Textile%20Ministry's%20website.%20Of%20these%2C%2040%25%20of%20garment%20imports%20are%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%2020%25%20from%20China.%20The%20dumping%20of%20textiles%20by%20China%20is%20being%20monitored%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20and%20anti-dumping%20duties%20have%20been%20imposed%20on%20Chinese%20viscose%20staple%20fibre%20and%20other%20raw%20materials.%20But%20the%20bigger%20problem%20is%20that%20of%20Indian%20apparel%20makers%20moving%20to%20Bangladesh%20and%20flooding%20the%20Indian%20market%20with%20cheap%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20is%20an%20obvious%20choice%20for%20apparel%20manufacturing%20given%20labour%20is%20much%20cheaper%20than%20in%20India.%20Electricity%20is%20cheap%20and%20Bangladesh%20has%20managed%20to%20snag%20lower%20duties%20in%20Western%20export%20markets%20than%20India%2C%20with%20many%20countries%20waiving%20duties%20on%20Bangladeshi%20apparel%20since%20it%20is%20a%20poor%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20even%20India%20has%20waived%20import%20duties%20on%20Bangladeshi%20apparel%2C%20which%20has%20made%20it%20more%20lucrative%20for%20Indians%20to%20manufacture%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20sell%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHike%20In%20Electricity%20Tariffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20insult%20to%20injury%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20in%20September%202022%20hiked%20electricity%20tariffs%20by%20introducing%20peak-hour%20charges%20and%20hiking%20demand%20charges.%20Then%2C%20in%20July%202023%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Electricity%20Regulatory%20Commission%20increased%20the%20retail%20electricity%20tariff%20for%20high-tension%20industrial%20consumers%20by%202.2%25.%20Despite%20agitations%20and%20protests%20by%20small%20business%20owners%2C%20no%20solution%20seems%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20cashflow%20hamstrung%2C%20the%20Finance%20Ministry's%20new%20rule%20of%20making%20payments%20to%20MSMEs%20within%2045%20days%20has%20hurt%20small%20business%20owners.%20Many%20MSMEs%20have%20also%20witnessed%20cancellation%20of%20orders%2C%20as%20the%20payment%20window%20has%20shrunk%20from%20the%20usual%20120%20to%20a%20180-day%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Tiruppur's%20garment%20industry%20is%20in%20the%20doldrums%20and%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20it%20will%20revive%20without%20strong%20support%20and%20intervention%20from%20governments%2C%20both%20State%20and%20Central.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20immediate%20need%20is%20to%20protect%20homegrown%20businesses%20by%20imposing%20import%20duties%20and%20tariffs%20as%20relevant.%20Power%20and%20tax%20incentives%20would%20also%20help.%20Tiruppur's%20exporters%20also%20want%20a%20Board%20that%20will%20help%20them%20navigate%20such%20rocky%20times.%20The%20road%20to%20recovery%20remains%20challenging%2C%20and%20the%20industry%20continues%20to%20face%20significant%20headwinds%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20regain%20its%20former%20glory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sandhya%20Ravishankar%20is%20a%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20th