ates-india-lok-sabha-elections-124030400087_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20has%20been%20hit%20with%20a%20fine%20of%20nearly%20%242%20billion%20by%20the%20European%20Commission%20over%20music%20streaming%20restrictions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224868%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apple%20logo%20displayed%20on%20a%20building%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a5193643bb77284b9d124b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223269%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20has%20been%20fined%20by%20the%20European%20Commission.%20%3Cp%3ENurPhoto%2F%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20European%20Commission%20fined%20Apple%201.8%20billion%20euros%20for%20abusing%20its%20market%20dominance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20restricted%20app%20developers%20from%20informing%20users%20about%20alternative%2C%20cheaper%20music%20services.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20plans%20to%20appeal%2C%20arguing%20the%20decision%20lacks%20credible%20evidence%20and%20benefits%20Spotify.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3EApple%20has%20been%20hit%20with%20a%20fine%20of%201.8%20billion%20euros%20(%241.95%20billion)%20by%20the%20European%20Commission%2C%20part%20of%20the%20European%20Union.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EApple%20was%20found%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Babusing%20its%20dominant%20position%20on%20the%20market%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20way%20it%20distributed%20music%20streaming%20platforms%20through%20its%20App%20Store%2C%20the%20body%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fcommission%2Fpresscorner%2Fdetail%2Fen%2Fip_24_1161%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20Monday.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Commission%20found%20that%20Apple%20applied%20restrictions%20on%20app%20developers%20preventing%20them%20from%20informing%20iOS%20users%20about%20alternative%20and%20cheaper%20music%20subscription%20services%20available%20outside%20of%20the%20app%2C%26quot%3B%20it%