m%20given%20Badarpur%2C%20while%20others%20are%20at%20better%20places.%20Let%20all%20the%20parties%20then%20relocate%20to%20Badarpur%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20using%20our%20good%20offices%20to%20get%20a%20plot.%20How%20can%20we%20permit%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20course%20of%20the%20arguments%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20also%20said%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20is%20his%20parent%20court.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20them%20to%20be%20denied%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20the%20Centre%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20said%20AAP%20must%20vacate%20the%20plot.%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20they%20hold%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20High%20Court%20to%20ransom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20last%20month%20pulled%20up%20AAP%20over%20the%20alleged%20encroachment.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20can%20take%20law%20into%20their%20own%20hands.%20How%20can%20a%20political%20party%20sit%20tight%20on%20that%3F%20Unencumbered%20possession%20must%20be%20given%20to%20the%20High%20Court.%20What%20will%20the%20High%20Court%20use%20it%20for%3F%20Only%20for%20the%20public%20and%20citizens.%20Why%20was%20the%20land%20then%20allotted%20to%20the%20High%20Court%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20took%20note%20of%20the%20matter%20while%20looking%20at%20cases%20related%20to%20judicial%20infrastructure%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20denied%20allegations%20of%20encroachment.%20It%20has%20said%20the%20plot%20was%20allotted%20to%20the%20party%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government.%C2%A0Mr%20Singhvi%20today%20said%20the%20plot%20was%20allotted%20to%20AAP%20in%202015.%20Amicus%20Curiae%20K%20Parmeshwar%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20plot%20was%20earmarked%20in%202022%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20family%20courts%2C%20and%20noted%20that%20nothing%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20to%20show%20that%20the%20land%20had%20been%20allotted%20to%20any%20political%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709553120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fde6qkv7_cji-singhvi_625x300_04_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-abhishek-singhvi-you-should-support-us-chief-justice-jokes-with-abhishek-singhvi-in-aap-case-5174305%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Intense%20arguments%20in%20the%20case%20related%20to%20AAP's%20alleged%20encroachment%20were%20interspersed%20with%20some%20humour%20when%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20told%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%20that%20he%20should%20not%20have%20appeared%20for%20the%20party%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-abhishek-singhvi-you-should-support-us-chief-justice-jokes-with-abhishek-singhvi-in-aap-case-5174305%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-abhishek-singhvi-you-should-support-us-chief-justice-jokes-with-abhishek-singhvi-in-aap-case-5174305%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-abhishek-singhvi-you-should-support-us-chief-justice-jokes-with-abhishek-singhvi-in-aap-case-5174305%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ashwin%20always%20trying%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20get%20you%20out%3A%20Root%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709553039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108207798%2Cimgsize-84086.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fengland-in-india%2Fashwin-always-trying-to-find-ways-to-get-you-out-joe-root%2Farticleshow%2F108207729.cms%22%2C%22summar