D%5C%221002%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ferrari%20stolen%20from%20F1%20driver%20Gerhard%20Berger%20was%20found%20after%2028%20years.%3Cp%3EMetropolitan%20Police%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EF1%20driver%20Gerhard%20Berger's%20stolen%20Ferrari%20F512M%20was%20recovered%20after%2028%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPolice%20believe%20the%20car%20was%20taken%20to%20Japan%20soon%20after%20it%20was%20stolen%2C%20and%20then%20shipped%20to%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENo%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%2C%20but%20the%20investigation%20by%20the%20UK's%20Met%20Police%20is%20ongoing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Ferrari%20stolen%20from%20Formula%201%20legend%20Gerhard%20Berger%20nearly%20three%20decades%20ago%20has%20been%20recovered%20by%20British%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerger%20was%20at%20the%20San%20Marino%20Grand%20Prix%20in%20Imola%2C%20Italy%2C%20in%20April%201995%20when%20his%20red%20Ferrari%20F512M%2C%20worth%20around%20%24443%2C500%2C%20went%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2010-time%20Grand%20Prix%20winner%20witnessed%20the%20car%20being%20driven%20away%20and%20attempted%20to%20chase%20the%20thief%20but%20could%20not%20catch%20them%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.standard.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fcrime%2Fformula-one-gerhard-berger-ferrari-stolen-san-marino-grand-prix-met-police-london-b1142918.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20London%20Evening%20Standard%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car%20was%20reported%20missing%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20trace%20of%20it%20until%20January%20of%20this%20year%2C%20when%20it%20was%20discovered%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.met.police.uk%2Fnews%2Forganised-vehicle-crime-unit-recover-ferrari-stolen-in-italy-28-years-ago-480340%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20by%20Britain's%20Metropolitan%20Police%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221777%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gerhard%20Berger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e5a62290413ab8e1d8b1b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGerhard%20Berger%20pictured%20at%20the%20Grand%20Prix%20of%20Monaco%20in%201988.%3Cp%3EPaul-Henri%20Cahier%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFerrari%20contacted%20the%20police%20in%20January%20after%20checks%20on%20the%20car%2C%20purchased%20by%20a%20US%20buyer%20via%20a%20UK%20broker%2C%20showed%20it%20was%20stolen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Organised%20Vehicle%20Crime%20Unit%20took%20four%20days%20to%20investigate%20the%20car's%20history%2C%20tracing%20back%2028%20years%20to%20when%20it%20was%20stolen%20from%20Berger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20enquiries%20were%20painstaking%20and%20included%20contacting%20authorities%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PC%20Mike%20Pilbeam%2C%20who%20led%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20worked%20quickly%20with%20partners%20including%20the%20National%20Crime%20Agency%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Ferrari%20and%20international%20car%20dealerships%2C%20and%20this%20collaboration%20was%20instrumental%20in%20understanding%20the%20vehicle's%20background%20and%20stopping%20it%20from%20leaving%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20showed%20the%20car%20had%20been%20shipped%20to%20Japan%20shortly%20after%20being%20stolen%20before%20being%20taken%20to%20the%20UK%20in%202023.%20No%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20theft%2C%20and%20an%20investigation%20is%20still%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car%20was%20originally%20taken%20during%20the%20same%20weekend%20as%20another%20F1%20driver's%20car%20was%20stolen.%20That%20car%20has%20yet%20to%20be%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Standard%2C%20the%20second%20stolen%20car%20was%20a%20silver-grey%20Ferrari%20355%20belonging%20to%20Jean%20Alesi%2C%20the%20French%20race%20driver%20w