%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20request%20the%20L%26amp%3BDO%20to%20process%20the%20application%20and%20communicate%20its%20decision%20within%20a%20period%20of%20four%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20D%20Y%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justices%20J%20B%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra.%20AAP%2C%20the%20bench%20added%2C%20has%20no%20lawful%20right%20to%20continue%20on%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20the%20court%20had%20observed%20that%20AAP%20was%20encroaching%20on%20the%20land%2C%20which%20was%20allotted%20to%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20for%20an%20expansion%20project%20--%20the%20building%20of%20additional%20court%20rooms%20for%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court.%20The%20top%20court%20took%20note%20of%20the%20matter%20while%20dealing%20with%20a%20case%20related%20to%20judicial%20infrastructure%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20court%20order%2C%20a%20meeting%20was%20held%20on%20February%2015%2C%20during%20which%20the%20state%20government%20had%20assured%20that%20the%20plot%20would%20be%20vacated%20in%20two%20months%2C%20provided%20an%20alternative%20plot%20was%20given.%20But%20the%20matter%20did%20not%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20angry%20judges%20questioned%20the%20lapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20no%20one%20can%20take%20the%20law%20into%20their%20own%20hands.%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20any%20political%20party%20sit%20on%20it%3F%20All%20encroachments%20will%20be%20removed...%20The%20High%20Court%20should%20be%20given%20possession%20of%20the%20land%2C%20which%20can%20be%20used%20for%20the%20public%20and%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Justice%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20direct%20that%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20PWD%20Secretary%20and%20Finance%20Secretary%20of%20Delhi%20Government%20should%20convene%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20Registrar%20General%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20before%20the%20next%20date%20to%20ensure%20resolution%20of%20all%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20questioned%20why%20AAP%20has%20to%20be%20given%20alternate%20land.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20want%20to%20evacuate%20then%20let%20them%20evacuate.%20What%20is%20this%20condition%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allocation%2C%20he%20added%2C%20was%20made%20to%20the%20government%20and%20it%20gave%20it%20to%20the%20party.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they%20have%20to%20evacuate%E2%80%A6%20How%20can%20they%20hold%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20High%20Court%20at%20ransom%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20AAP%2C%20said%20as%20one%20of%20the%20six%20national%20parties%2C%20AAP%20is%20entitled%20to%20a%20plot%20of%20land%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20in%20a%20lighter%20vein%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20should%20not%20appear%20in%20this%20case%2C%20you%20cannot%20oppose%20the%20ground%20for%20Delhi%20High%20Court%E2%80%A6%20You%20are%20using%20our%20good%20offices%20to%20get%20the%20plot%E2%80%A6%20How%20can%20we%20allow%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20earlier%20hearing%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20criticised%20the%20Delhi%20government%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bindifferent%20attitude%26quot%3B%20towards%20providing%20funds%20for%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20Delhi%20district%20judiciary.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20had%20said%20approval%20had%20been%20granted%20for%20three%20of%20the%20four%20projects%20by%20March%202021.%20Funds%2C%20however%2C%20were%20yet%20to%20be%20released%20for%20these%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709549940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-06%2Faap-office_650x400_71497503030.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvacate-land-kept-for-judicial-infra-by-june-15-supreme-court-orders-aap-5173