nkled%20salt%20on%20our%20wounds.%E2%80%9D%20They%20decided%20to%20oppose%20the%20BJP%20and%20Teni%20both%20in%20the%20general%20election%20and%20call%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%9Cpro-corporate%2C%20anti-farmers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%203%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20BJP%20released%20the%20names%20of%20195%20candidates%20from%2016%20states%20and%20two%20Union%20territories.%20Teni%20is%20a%20junior%20minister%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20home%20department.%20Junior%20minister%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Ashish%20Mishra%2C%20is%20charged%20with%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20incident%2C%20which%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20four%20farmers%20and%20a%20journalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%2C%20an%20umbrella%20body%20of%20several%20farmer%20unions%2C%20believes%20two-term%20parliamentarian%20Teni%20was%20a%20conspirator%20in%20the%20Lakhimpur-Kheri%20incident%20and%20has%20been%20putting%20pressure%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20for%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20from%20the%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20The%20demand%20for%20his%20resignation%20is%20also%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20farmer%20protest%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Flakhimpur-kheri-bjp-ashish-mishra-rule-of-law%5C%22%3EIn%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%2C%20BJP%20Proves%20India%20Has%20No%20Rule%20of%20Law%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrked%20farmer%20leaders%20demanded%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20top%20brass%20withdraw%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20candidature%20or%20face%20the%20consequences%20of%20betraying%20farmers%20in%20the%20next%20elections.%20According%20to%20Ashish%20Mittal%2C%20executive%20member%20of%20the%20SKM%20coordination%20committee%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20under%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20rule%2C%20alleged%20criminals%20like%20Teni%20and%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20thrive%20while%20poor%20students%2C%20women%2C%20labourers%2C%20and%20farmers%20face%20state-sponsored%20repression.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMittal%20is%20concerned%20about%20the%20future%20of%20democracy%20in%20the%20country%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%20giving%20a%20ticket%20to%20Teni%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20sent%20a%20loud%20and%20clear%20message%20that%20if%20it%20retains%20power%20in%202024%2C%20it%20will%20crush%20all%20democratic%20movements.%E2%80%9D%20Mittal%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sabha%2C%20is%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20hypocrisy%20for%20honouring%20the%20pro-farmer%20agronomist%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratan%20award%20while%20also%20supporting%20a%20candidate%20responsible%20for%20the%20deaths%20of%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20farmer%20leader%2C%20Mukut%20Singh%2C%20the%20national%20joint%20secretary%20of%20All%20India%20Kisan%20Sabha%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20farmers%20will%20not%20retreat%20from%20their%20demand%20at%20any%20cost%20to%20register%20a%20first%20information%20report%20against%20Teni%20in%20the%20Lakhimpur-Kheri%20case%20under%20Section%20120-B%20(Criminal%20Conspiracy)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20numerous%20nationwide%20protests%20organised%20by%20farmers%20against%20Teni%2C%20Singh%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CHis%20candidacy%20exemplifies%20the%20anti-democratic%20stance%20of%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%20The%20farmer%20leader%20continued%20by%20stating%20that%20the%20SKM%20will%20urge%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20to%20vote%20against%20the%20anti-farmer%20BJP%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20tragic%20reminiscence%20of%20the%20Lakhimpur%20incident%20remains%20alive%20in%20our%20hearts.%20The%20BJP%20hurt%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20sentiments%20by%20giving%20tickets%20to%20Teni%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20K.%20Krishnaprasad%2C%20AKIS%E2%80%99%20finance%20secretary.%20When%20questioned%20about%20the%20political%20impacts%20of%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20candidature%2C%20farmer%20leader%20K.%20Krishnaprasad%20stated%20that%20farmers%20all%20over%20the%20nation%2C%20not%20just%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20are%20furious%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decision%20%E2%80%93%20now%20farmers%20are%20overthrowing%20this%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20arrogant%20government%20in%20the%20next%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20farmers%20of%20Lakhimpur-Kheri%20are%20also%20upset%20and%20want%20the%20BJP%20to%20reconsider%20its%20decision.%20Following%20the%20release%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20list%2C%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Kisaan%20Union%20was%20convened%2C%20according%20to%20Dilbhag%20Singh%20%E2%80%9CSindhu%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20district%20president%20of%20the%20union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20protested%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20candidature%20and%20demanded%20that%20Modi%20replace%20him%20with%20another%20candidate.%20%E2%80%9CAstonishingly%2C%20a%20man%20who%20should%20be%20imprisoned%20for%20his%20heinous%20conspiracy%20against%20farmers%20is%20going%20to%20contest%20for%20office%20on%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20disgruntled%20farmer%20leader%20Sindhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIshwari%20Prasad%20Kushwaha%2C%20secretary%20of%20Kisaan%20Mahasabha%20(Tikait)%2C%20views%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20field%20Teni%20from%20Lakimpur-Kheri%20as%20mocking%20crores%20of%20Indian%20farmers%2C%20while%20they%20persist%20in%20demanding%20his%20resignation.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20farmers%20are%20angry%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20they%20plan%20to%20raise%20the%20Lakhimpur-Kheri%20issue%20at%20the%20Mahapanchayat%20on%20March%2014%20at%20Ramlila%20Ground%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%20promised%20to%20double%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20in%202014%2C%20but%20after%20getting%20power%2C%20put%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20issues%20like%20the%20demand%20of%20MSP%2C%20etc.%20on%20the%20back%20burner%20and%20turned%20blind%20eyes%20towards%20their%20plights%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kushwaha.%20Anguished%20farmers%20would%20upset%20the%20apple%20cart%20of%20the%20BJP%20because%20it%20has%20been%20dancing%20to%20corporate%20tunes%20and%20repressing%20farmers%20for%20a%20decade%20since%20coming%20to%20power%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20recalled%20that%20on%20October%203%2C%202021%2C%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20son%E2%80%99s%20convoy%20allegedly%20rammed%20three%20farmers%20and%20a%20journalist%20in%20Tikunia%2C%20Lakhimpur-Kheri.%20The%20deceased%20farmers%20were%20returning%20from%20protesting%20three%20Modi%20government%20farm%20laws%20when%20the%20incident%20occurred.%20Later%20on%2C%20after%20a%20long%20and%20massive%20farmer%20protest%2C%20the%20government%20repealed%20these%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20in%20the%20Lakimpur-Kheri%20district%20say%20that%20Teni%2C%20who%20is%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%2C%20went%20to%20an%20event%20in%20Palia%2C%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20district%2C%20in%20September%202021.%20Some%20members%20of%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20union%20waved%20black%20flags%20as%20a%20protest%20during%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20farmers%2C%20after%20this%20protest%2C%20Tani%20purportedly%20plotted%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20assassinate%20the%20farmers%20for%20protesting%20against%20the%20controversial%20farm%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeni%20allegedly%20intimidated%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20during%20his%20speech%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CSudhar%20jao%2C%20nahi%20toh%20hum%20sudhaar%20denge%2C%20do%20minute%20me.%E2%80%9D%20(You%20better%20change%20your%20ways%2C%20or%20we%E2%80%99ll%20teach%20you%20a%20lesson%20in%20two%20minutes.)%20Rough%20translation%20from%20Hindi.%20A%20video%20of%20his%20speech%20went%20viral%20following%20the%20Lakimpur-Kheri%20incident.%20Farmers%20accuse%20Teni%20of%20orchestrating%20a%20conspiracy%20based%20on%20his%20speech%20and%20want%20him%20to%20step%20down%20as%20minister.%20They%20also%20want%20the%20government%20to%20prosecute%20him%20for%20the%20Lakhimpur%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709549398000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04154105%2FUntitled-design-24-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flakhimpur-kheri-violence-farmers-miffed-over-conspirator-tenis-name-on-bjps-ls-nominee-list%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farmers'%20unions%20allege%20that%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Mishra%20'Teni'%20and%20his%20son%20Ashish%20Mishra%20are%20co-conspirators%20in%20the%20October%203%2C%202021%20violence%2C%20which%20killed%20eight%20people%20and%20injured%2010.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flakhimpur-kheri-violence-farmers-miffed-over-conspirator-tenis-name-on-bjps-ls-nominee-list%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cadila%20Pharmaceuticals%20launches%20Tetra%20vaccine%20to%20prevent%20influenza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709549188000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-01%2F19%2Ffull%2F1674097211-0177.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcadila-pharmaceuticals-launches-tetra-vaccine-to-prevent-influenza-124030400592_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Developed%20using%20proprietary%20technology%20employing%20nano-sized%20particles%2C%20the%20vaccine%20mimics%20the%20external%20structure%20of%20the%20virus%20without%20containing%20intact%20genetic%20material%2C%20company%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2F