esandnoble.com%252Fw%252Feducation-is-freedom-james-w-keyes%252F1144034017%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEducation%20is%20Freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhich%20came%20out%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20Keyes'%20daily%20routine%20based%20on%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeyes%20said%20he%20would%20usually%20wake%20up%20around%205%3A30%20a.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20admitted%20that%20he's%20not%20%26quot%3Bnaturally%20a%20morning%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20role%20required%20him%20to%20become%20one.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20day%20is%20a%20new%20adventure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20often%20anxious%20to%20wake%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%206%20a.m.%2C%20he'd%20typically%20be%20onto%20his%20morning%20workout%2C%20usually%20a%20combination%20of%20cardio%20and%20weights%20in%20his%20home%20gym.%20He'd%20have%20breakfast%20before%20or%20after%20his%20workout%20and%20opt%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-trying-ways-to-upgrade-frozen-waffles%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEggo%20waffles%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20scrambled%20egg%20whites%20with%20fresh%20jalape%C3%B1os.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBy%207%3A30%20a.m.%20he'd%20begin%20sorting%20through%20his%20inbox.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKeyes%20said%20he%20liked%20to%20filter%20through%20his%20inbox%20himself.%20%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20have%20emails%20when%20I%20first%20started%20my%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20were%20corresponding%20by%20the%20telephone%20or%20even%20letters.%26quot%3B%20Keyes%20said%20that%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femail-strategies-to-stop-your-messages-from-being-ignored%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemails%20are%20exchanged%20at%20a%20comparatively%20faster%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20still%20sees%20them%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20communications%20device%26quot%3B%20for%20sensitive%20or%20pressing%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%2C%20he'd%20also%20scan%20through%20major%20new%20outlets%20to%20keep%20abreast%20of%20the%20day's%20major%20headlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%209%20a.m.%20to%20noon%20he%20be%20in%20regular%20standing%20meetings.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKeyes%20said%20the%20first%20half%20of%20his%20day%20usually%20revolved%20around%20more%20structured%20tasks%20in%20which%20he%20and%20his%20senior%20staff%20focused%20on%20establishing%20weekly%20priorities.%20He'd%20also%20outline%20communications%20with%20the%20company's%20board%2C%20vendors%2C%20and%20field%20operations%20teams%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%2C%20a%20big%20portion%20of%20the%20CEO's%20job%20is%20communications%2C%26quot%3B%20Keyes%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20found%20that%20the%20communications%20piece%20was%20critically%20important%2C%20especially%20in%20times%20of%20change%2C%20when%20fear%20sets%20in%2C%20and%20the%20organization%20lacks%20the%20confidence%20to%20continue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20when%20you're%20heading%20a%20massive%20organization%2C%20supported%20by%20several%20layers%20of%20management%2C%20communication%20can%20often%20feel%20like%20a%20game%20of%20telephone%2C%20he%20said.%20Keyes'%20tactic%20was%20to%20take%20a%20page%20from%20Walmart%20founder%20Sam%20Walton's%20playbook%20and%20maintain%20a%20direct%20communication%20channel%20with%20the%20broader%20company.%20For%20example%2C%20Keyes%20said%20he'd%20communicate%20three%20priorities%20with%207-Eleven's%20convenience%20stores%20nationwide%20through%20a%20weekly%20video%20conference%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Beveryone%20was%20on%20the%20same%20page.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20important%20component%20of%20Keyes'%20morning%20routine%20would%20be%20fresh%20food%20sampling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20constantly%20searching%20around%20the%20globe%20for%20new%20food%20trends%2C%20new%20trends%20in%20convenience%20that%20might%20excite%20our%20customers%20and%20find%20those%2C%20bring%20them%20in%2C%20either%20rebrand%20them%20in%20our%20own%20brand%2C%20or%20roll%20them%20out%2C%20and%20test%20them%20in%20the%20stores%2C%26quot%3B%20Keyes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20week%2C%20a%20new%20item%20would%20usually%20be%20introduced%20in-store%20once%20a%20week%2C%20so%20Keyes%20and%20his%20team%20felt%20it%20was%20important%20to%20sample%20it%20and%20provide%20feedback.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20tough%20on%20the%20diet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20laughing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELunch%20might%20be%20a%20Slurpee%2C%20a%20sampling%20of%20fresh%20food%2C%20or%20salad%20on%20the%20go.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKeyes%20said%20he%20usually%20didn't%20have%20time%20for%20a%20lunch%20break.%20So%2C%20if%20it%20wasn't%20a%20sampling%20day%2C%20he'd%20usually%20have%20a%20salad%20brought%20in%2C%20and%20eat%20it%20between%20meetings.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20Keyes%20said%20he%20had%20a%20Slurpee%20machine%20installed%20in%20his%20office.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-slurpees-for-7-eleven-day-ranked-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESlurpees%20are%20frozen%2C%20carbonated%20drinks%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20have%20practically%20become%20synonymous%20with%20the%207-Eleven%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20thought%2C%20wouldn't%20it%20be%20fun%20to%20have%20a%20Slurpee%20machine%20in%20my%20office%3F%20Sounds%20like%20a%20great%20idea%2C%20and%20that%20way%20I%20can%20sample%20a%20Slurpee%20every%20day%2C%20different%20flavors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20seemed%20like%20a%20great%20way%20to%20entertain%20guests.%20%26quot%3BI%20hadn't%20thought%20about%20the%20calorie%20content%2C%20but%20that%20sparked%20the%20initiative%20to%20say%2C%20'let's%20try%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20low%20calorie%20or%20zero%20calorie%20frozen%2C%20carbonated%2