le%22%3A%22This%20AI%20Worm%20Can%20Steal%20Data%2C%20Break%20Security%20Of%20ChatGPT%20And%20Gemini%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20generative%20AI%20systems%20like%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20and%20Google's%20Gemini%20become%20more%20advanced%2C%20researchers%20are%20now%20developing%20AI%20worms%20which%20can%20steal%20your%20confidential%20data%20and%20break%20security%20measures%20of%20the%20generative%20AI%20systems%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20Wired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20Cornell%20University%2C%20Technion-Israel%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20and%20Intuit%20created%20the%20first%20generative%20AI%20worm%20called%20'Morris%20II'%20which%20can%20steal%20data%20or%20deploy%20malware%20and%20spread%20from%20one%20system%20to%20another.%20It%20has%20been%20named%20after%20the%20first%20worm%20which%20was%20launched%20on%20the%20internet%20in%201988.%20Ben%20Nassi%2C%20a%20Cornell%20Tech%20researcher%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20basically%20means%20that%20now%20you%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20conduct%20or%20to%20perform%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20cyberattack%20that%20hasn't%20been%20seen%20before%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20worm%20can%20breach%20some%20security%20measures%20in%20ChatGPT%20and%20Gemini%20by%20attacking%20a%20generative%20AI%20email%20assistant%20with%20the%20intent%20of%20stealing%20email%20data%20and%20sending%20spam%2C%20as%20per%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20used%20an%20%26quot%3Badversarial%20self-replicating%20prompt%26quot%3B%20to%20develop%20the%20generative%20AI%20worm.%20According%20to%20them%2C%20this%20prompt%20causes%20the%20generative%20AI%20model%20to%20generate%20a%20different%20prompt%20in%20response.%20To%20execute%20it%2C%20the%20researchers%20then%20created%20an%20email%20system%20that%20could%20send%20and%20receive%20messages%20using%20generative%20AI%2C%20adding%20into%20ChatGPT%2C%20Gemini%2C%20and%20open-source%20LLM.%20Further%2C%20they%20discovered%20two%20ways%20to%20utilise%20the%20system-%20by%20using%20a%20self-replicating%20prompt%20that%20was%20text-based%20and%20by%20embedding%20the%20question%20within%20an%20image%20file.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20case%2C%20the%20researchers%20took%20on%20the%20role%20of%20attackers%20and%20sent%20an%20email%20with%20an%20adversarial%20text%20prompt.%20This%20%26quot%3Bpoisons%26quot%3B%20the%20email%20assistant's%20database%20by%20utilising%20retrieval-augmented%20generation%2C%20which%20allows%20LLMs%20to%20get%20more%20data%20from%20outside%20their%20system.%20According%20to%20Mr%20Nassi%2C%20the%20retrieval-augmented%20generation%20%26quot%3Bjailbreaks%20the%20GenAI%20service%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20retrieves%20an%20email%20in%20response%20to%20a%20user%20inquiry%20and%20sends%20it%20to%20GPT-4%20or%20Gemini%20Pro%20to%20generate%20a%20response.%20This%20eventually%20results%20in%20the%20theft%20of%20data%20from%20the%20emails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20generated%20response%20containing%20the%20sensitive%20user%20data%20later%20infects%20new%20hosts%20when%20it%20is%20used%20to%20reply%20to%20an%20email%20sent%20to%20a%20new%20client%20and%20then%20stored%20in%20the%20database%20of%20the%20new%20client%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20second%20method%2C%20the%20researcher%20mentioned%2C%20%26quot%3BBy%20encoding%20the%20self-replicating%20prompt%20into%20the%20image%2C%20any%20kind%20of%20image%20containing%20spam%2C%20abuse%20material%2C%20or%20even%20propaganda%20can%20be%20forwarded%20further%20to%20new%20clients%20after%20the%20initial%20email%20has%20been%20sent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20showcasing%20the%20findings%20shows%20the%20email%20system%20repeatedly%20forwarding%20a%20message.%20The%20researchers%20claim%20that%20they%20could%20also%20obtain%20email%20data.%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20names%2C%20it%20can%20be%20telephone%20numbers%2C%20credit%20card%20numbers%2C%20SSN%2C%20anything%20that%20is%20considered%20confidential%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nassi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FFL3qHH02Yd4%3Fsi%3DOL3xySjMo1ccWPn8%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20also%20warned%20about%20%26quot%3Bbad%20architecture%20design%26quot%3B%20within%20the%20AI%20system.%20They%20also%20reported%20their%20observations%20to%20Google%20and%20OpenAI.%20%26quot%3BThey%20appear%20to%20have%20found%20a%20way%20to%20exploit%20prompt-injection%20type%20vulnerabilities%20by%20relying%20on%20user%20input%20that%20hasn't%20been%20checked%20or%20filtered%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20OpenAI%20told%20the%20outlet.%20Further%2C%20they%20mentioned%20that%20they%20are%20working%20to%20make%20systems%20%26quot%3Bmore%20resilient%26quot%3B%20and%20developers%20should%20%26quot%3Buse%20methods%20that%20ensure%20they%20are%20not%20working%20with%20harmful%20input.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709548140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F5b5nrh3o_ai_625x300_04_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthis-ai-worm-can-steal-data-break-security-of-chatgpt-and-gemini-5173985%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20researchers%20used%20an%20%26quot%3Badversarial%20self-replicating%20prompt%26quot%3B%20to%20develop%20the%20generative%20AI%20worm.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthis-ai-worm-can-steal-data-break-security-of-chatgpt-and-gemini-5173985%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20orders%20AAP%20to%20vacate%20its%20Delhi%20HQ%20by%20June%2015%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709548104