ral%20polls%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20which%20had%20been%20fraudulently%20decided%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20%E2%80%93%20and%20declared%20the%20AAP-Congress%20joint%20candidate%20Kuldeep%20Kumar%20the%20validly%20elected%20city%20mayor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20beleaguered%20Congress-AAP%20alliance%2C%20which%20fought%20a%20legal%20battle%20in%20the%20SC%20to%20wrest%20the%20mayor%E2%80%99s%20post%20from%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20grasp%2C%20was%20heavily%20relying%20on%20the%20defected%20AAP%20councillors%20to%20return%20the%20party%20fold%20to%20win%20the%20remaining%20two%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20made%20attempts%20to%20win%20them%20over%20but%20they%20remained%20incommunicado%20and%20stayed%20with%20BJP%2C%20finally%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20victory%20of%20their%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20development%2C%20AAP%20Chandigarh%20leader%20Prem%20Garg%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20AAP-Congress%20alliance%20had%20been%20poised%20to%20win%20these%20seats%20and%20would%20have%20done%20so%20if%20the%20BJP-appointed%20presiding%20officer%20Anil%20Masih%20had%20not%20engineered%20blatant%20rigging%20during%20January%2030%20mayoral%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanil-masih-admits-marking-ballots-cji-says-he-must-be-prosecuted%5C%22%3EChandigarh%20Mayor%20Election%3A%20Presiding%20Officer%20Admits%20Marking%20Ballots%2C%20CJI%20Says%20He%20Must%20Be%20Prosecuted%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20BJP%20has%20no%20moral%20right%20to%20celebrate%20their%20victory%20in%20these%20seats%20since%20they%20won%20it%20because%20of%20horse%20trading%20and%20unfair%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20was%20held%20under%20chairmanship%20of%20AAP-Congress%20mayor%20Kuldeep%20Kumar%2C%20who%20carefully%20supervised%20each%20and%20every%20vote%20cast.%20Voting%20was%20held%20