ll%20attempt%20to%20sabotage%20agendas%20and%20other%20daily%20businesses%20of%20the%20MC%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20BJP%20also%20enjoys%20more%20strength%20against%20its%20counterparts%20in%20MC%20house%2C%20making%20it%20easy%C2%A0to%20pass%20or%20reject%20any%20agenda%20to%20be%20tabled%20by%20the%20AAP-Congress%20mayor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20immediate%20concern%20for%20both%20the%20parties%20is%20to%20win%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20Chandigarh%20parliamentary%20seat%20will%20have%20a%20Congress%20candidate%20as%20per%20the%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20pact%20between%20Congress%20and%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709547643000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F19085919%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-8.58.44-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fchandigarh-mayoral-polls-after-sc-slam-aap-defections-allow-bjp-to-clinch-two-top-posts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fresh%20polls%20to%20these%20posts%20were%20necessitated%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20month%20overturned%20the%20results%20of%20the%20rigged%20elections%20and%20said%20that%20AAP-Congress%20candidate%20Kuldeep%20Kumar%20is%20the%20mayor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fchandigarh-mayoral-polls-after-sc-slam-aap-defections-allow-bjp-to-clinch-two-top-posts%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vipul%20Organics%20bags%20Rs%207.15%20cr%20worth%20order%20from%20TNPL%20to%20supply%20pigment%20dye%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709547566000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F08%2Ffull%2F1680943423-4068.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fvipul-organics-bags-rs-7-15-cr-worth-order-from-tnpl-to-supply-pigme