20response%20to%20a%20question%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fpm-modi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BPlatforms%20like%20Google%20are%20significant%20powers%20on%20the%20internet%20(and)%20for%20them%20to%20do%20something%20wrong%20and%20then%20simply%20say%2C%20'I'm%20sorry'%20or%20'I%20apologise'%20is%20certainly%20not%20what%20the%20law%20expects%20them%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20questioned%20the%20release%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Buntested%20platform%20(referring%20to%20the%20Gemini%20chatbot)...%20without%20any%20disclosures%20or%20disclaimers%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20then%20there%20will%20be%20consequences.%20To%20simply%20then%20say%20'...%20sorry%2C%20it%20was%20untested'%20is%20not%20consistent%20with%20our%20expectations%20of%20compliance%20with%20the%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20there%20a%20belief%20amongst%20these%20big%20platforms%20that%20they%20can%20take%20something%20from%20the%20lab...%20and%20launch%20it%20without%20guardrails%20or%20protective%20framework.%20This%20is%20unconscionable%20and%20unacceptable...%20given%20not%20just%20the%20law%20but%20even%C2%A0%20a%20sense%20of%20responsibility%20and%20discipline%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chandrasekhar%20emphasised%20the%20government's%20%26quot%3Bsincere%20(and)%20serious%20responsibility%26quot%3B%20to%20internet%20users%20in%20India%2C%20and%20said%20tech%20companies%20could%20not%20%26quot%3Bget%20away%20by%20talking%20their%20way%20out%20of%20a%20problem%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20stopped%20short%20of%20saying%20the%20government%20does%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20plan%20to%20prosecute%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Minister%20cited%20the%20new%20IT%20Rules%20and%20said%20tech%20companies%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20allow%20their%20platforms%20to%20be%20used%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20outputs%20unlawful%20content%20or%20violates%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%2C%20though%2C%20say%20if%20the%20government%20will%20actually%20take%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20is%20not%20so%20much%20for%20the%20government%20to%20prosecute%20as%20much%20as%20the%20users%20who%20have%20the%20cause%20of%20action...%20who%20are%20prejudiced%20by%20a%20platform%20that%20spews%20out%20unlawful%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20heard...%20there%20are%20many%20people%20who%20are%20quite%20agitated%20by%20the%20conduct%20of%20this%20and%20other%20platforms.%20My%20response%20to%20them%20is%2C%20'the%20government%20may%2C%20or%20may%20not%2C%20do%20some%20things%20because%20we%20have%20limited%20powers%20under%20the%20law...%20it%20is%20for%20individuals%2C%20or%20groups%2C%20to%20hold%20them%20to%20account.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chandrasekhar's%20sharp%20words%20come%20amid%20a%20growing%20row%20between%20the%20government%20and%20Google%20after%20Gemini%20-%20a%20generative%20artificial%20intelligence%20chatbot%20earlier%20called%20Bard%20-%20after%20the%20tool's%20controversial%20response%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20his%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGemini%20reportedly%20based%20its%20answer%20on%20factors%20like%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20%26quot%3Bnationalist%20ideology%26quot%3B%20and%20what%20its%20critics%20say%20is%20quashing%20of%20dissent%20and%20violence%20against%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder-fire%2C%20Google%20last%20month%20conceded%20Gemini%20%26quot%3Bmay%20not%20always%20be%20reliable%20in%20responding%20to%20certain%20prompts%20related%20to%20current%20events%20and%20political%20topics%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%20it%20was%20working%20to%20address%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgoogle-pauses-ai-tool-after-it-creates-images-of-black-woman-nazi-soldiers-5107012%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Pauses%20AI%20Tool%20Over%20Images%20Of%20Woman%20Nazi%20Soldiers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20just%20the%20Modi%20question%20that%20has%20the%20chatbot%20roiled%20in%20controversy.%20Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20said%20last%20week%20some%20of%20its%20text%20and%20image%20responses%20were%20%26quot%3Bbiased%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20unacceptable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsundar-pichai-slams-completely-unacceptable-gemini-ai-gaffes-5143585%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGemini%20AI%20Gaffes%20%26quot%3BCompletely%20Unacceptable%26quot%3B%3A%20Google's%20Sundar%20Pichai%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20after%20Gemini%2C%20asked%20to%20show%20the%20founding%20fathers%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20generated%20photos%20of%20people%20of%20colour%2C%20including%20a%20man%20of%20apparent%20Sikh%20heritage%2C%20in%20a%20significant%20historical%20faux%20pas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20aware%20Gemini%20is%20offering%20inaccuracies%20in%20some%20historical%20image%20generation%20depictions...%20we%20are%20working%20to%20improve%20these%20kinds%20of%20depictions%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGemini's%20AI%20image%20generation%20does%20generate%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20people.%20And%20that's%20generally%20a%20good%20thing%20because%20people%20around%20the%20world%20use%20it.%20But%20it's%20missing%20the%20mark%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20all%20of%20these%20concerns%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20is%20expected%20to%20issue%20a%20notice