ntry%20ko%20importance%20%3Cem%3Enahi%20de%20rahe%3C%2Fem%3E.%20(Earn%20money%2C%20who%20is%20stopping%20you%3F%20But%20it%20shouldn't%20be%20like%20you%20are%20not%20playing%20for%20the%20country%20or%20domestic%20cricket).%20This%20thing%20is%20now%20firmly%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20players.%20%3Cem%3EMai%20ek%20mahine%20pehle%20rest%20kar%20lunga%2C%20fir%20IPL%20khel%20lunga.%20Ye%20mentally%20hota%20hai%2C%20ki%20mai%20itne%20paise%20kaise%20chodun%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Will%20rest%20for%20a%20month%20before%20the%20IPL%20and%C2%A0then%20play.%20This%20happens%20because%20mentally%20you%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20let%20go%20of%20that%20money).%20But%20this%20is%20not%20fair%20at%20all.%20A%20player%20needs%20to%20balance%20things.%20Money%20is%20important%2C%20but%20this%20(giving%20franchise%20cricket%20the%20priority)%20is%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0could%20manage%20to%20score%20just%203%20runs%20off%208%20balls%20before%20he%20was%20clean%20bowled%20by%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sandeep%20Warrier%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63795-sankarankutty-sandeep-warrier-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESandeep%20Warrier%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0during%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20semi-final%20match%20between%20Mumbai%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Iyer's%20first%20domestic%20match%20after%20he%20was%20not%20given%20a%20central%20contract%20by%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI).%20The%20decision%20has%20created%20quite%20stir%20among%20both%20fans%20and%20experts%20alike%20with%20many%20thinking%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20exclude%20Iyer%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20correct%20and%20it%20can%20serve%20as%20an%20example%20for%20younger%20cricketers%20who%20may%20look%20to%20prioritise%20the%20IPL%20over%20playing%20red-ball%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709546220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fsm30qqc8_ishan-kishan-shreyas-iyer_625x300_28_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fearn-money-but-aise-bhi-nahi-ishan-kishan-shreyas-iyer-delivered-blunt-message-5173798%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Praveen%20Kumar%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20and%20Ishan%20Kishan%20not%20receiving%20central%20contracts%20from%20the%20BCCI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sanatana%20Dharma%20Case%3A%20%E2%80%98Should%E2%80%99ve%20Known%20the%20Consequences%2C%E2%80%99%20SC%20Tells%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04213611%2FUdhayanidhi.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20(March%204)%20rebuked%20Tamil%20Nadu%20minister%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20for%20his%20remarks%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%20while%20hearing%20his%20petition%20to%20club%20the%20FIRs%20against%20him%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStalin%2C%20who%20had%20compared%20sanatana%20dharma%20to%20a%20disease%20during%20a%20speech%20in%20September%2C%202023%2C%20has%20been%20booked%20in%20six%20states%2C%20including%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bench%2C%20consisting%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20petition%2C%20asked%20him%20to%20move%20the%20respective%20high%20courts%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%9DYou%20abuse%20your%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20right.%20You%20abuse%20your%20Article%2025%20right.%20Now%20you%20are%20exercising%20your%20Article%2032%20right%3F%20Do%20you%20not%20know%20the%20consequences%20of%20what%20you%20said%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStalin%E2%80%99s%20counsel%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20replied%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20to%20move%20six%20high%20courts%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20constantly%20be%20tied%20up%20in%20this%E2%80%A6This%20is%20persecution%20before%20the%20prosecution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Datta%20then%20reiterated%20his%20disapproval%20of%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20comments%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20not%20a%20layman.%20You%20are%20a%20minister.%20You%20should%20know%20the%20consequences.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESinghvi%20relied%20on%20precedents%20involving%20Amish%20Devgan%2C%20Arnab%20Goswami%2C%20Nupur%20Sharma%2C%20and%20Mohammed%20Zubair%2C%20where%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20allowed%20the%20consolidation%20of%20FIRs%20in%20multiple%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20counsel%20argued%20that%20the%20cause%20of%20action%20in%20the%20FIRs%20was%20the%20same%2C%20stemming%20from%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20minister%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20remarks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20much%20persuasion%2C%20the%20bench%20agreed%20to%20examine%20the%20plea%20and%20scheduled%20the%20next%20hearing%20for%20the%20following%20Friday%2C%20asking%20Singhvi%20to%20present%20relevant%20precedents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStalin%E2%80%99s%20remark%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStalin%2C%20a%20DMK%20leader%20and%20son%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20chief%20minister%20MK%20Stalin%2C%20got%20mired%20in%20controversy%20last%20September%20for%20comparing%2