%3B%3A%20Big%20Order%20On%20Legal%20Shield%20For%20MPs%2C%20MLAs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20independently%20adjudicated%20on%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20controversy.%20Do%20Parliamentarians%20enjoy%20immunity%3F%20We%20disagree%20and%20overrule%20the%20majority%20on%20this%20aspect%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20Case%20Background%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress-led%20alliance%20that%20came%20to%20power%20after%20the%201991%20general%20election%20was%20a%20minority%20administration%3B%20riding%20the%20tail%20end%20of%20a%20wave%20of%20sympathy%20following%20ex-Prime%20Minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20assassination%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%20232%20of%20the%20487%20seats%2C%20below%20the%20majority%20mark%20of%20272.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao's%20tenure%20saw%20multiple%20challenges%2C%20including%20a%20major%20financial%20crisis%20that%20triggered%20the%201991%20economic%20liberalisation%20policies%20that%20was%20a%20political%20hot%20potato.%20The%20government%20also%20faced%20criticism%20for%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20in%20December%201992%2C%20and%20the%20communal%20violence%20that%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20back%20of%20these%2C%20the%20opposition%20introduced%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20in%20July%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpv-narasimha-rao-a-debated-legacy-now-bharat-ratna-5024235%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPV%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20A%20Debated%20Legacy%2C%20Now%20Bharat%20Ratna%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20at%20the%20time%20had%20251%20votes%2C%20including%20those%20from%20other%20parties%20offering%20external%20support.%20This%20left%20the%20party%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20short%20of%20simple%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20voting%20took%20place%2