end%20a%20secret%20cause%20because%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20and%20it%20may%20be%20illegal%2C%20nobody%20will%20go%20against%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20You%20know%2C%20you%20said%20something%20that%20I%20think%20is%20particularly%20new%20and%20important-%20you%20said%20India%20has%20a%20deeper%20state%2C%20and%20this%20is%20different%20to%20the%20front%20facade%20of%20the%20official%20state.%20That%20there%20is%20a%20distinction%20between%20what%20happens%20officially%2C%20and%20what%20happens%20unofficially%2C%20and%20even%20illegally.%20A%20deeper%20state%20is%20terminology%20we%E2%80%99re%20used%20to%20associating%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20where%20the%20military%20establishment%20is%20the%20deeper%20state%2C%20and%20the%20civilian%20politicians%20is%20the%20facade.%20But%20you%E2%80%99re%20suggesting%20something%20akin%2C%20not%20similar%20but%20akin%2C%20is%20happening%20here%3B%20there%20is%20the%20S%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eangh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Parivar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20vigilantes%2C%20the%20cow%20lynchers%2C%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20deeper%20state%2C%20there%20are%20the%20BJP%20civilian%20politicians%20that%20are%20the%20front%20facade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20your%20deeper%20state%20is%20different%20from%20a%20deep%20state%3B%20indeed%20a%20deep%20state%20is%20largely%20associated%20with%20intelligence%20services%2C%20who%20are%20acting%20behind%20the%20curtain%2C%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20mean%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20there%20in%20India%20also.%20But%20a%20deeper%20state%20is%20different%20because%20it%20has%20a%20societal%20dimension%3B%20the%20state%20is%20there%20but%20relates%20and%20protect%2C%20people%20who%20are%20doing%20the%20cultural%20policy%20in%20at%20the%20societal%20level%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20Muslim%20boys%20do%20not%20talk%20to%20Hindu%20girls%20on%20the