dia%20into%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu%20Rashtra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20did%20not%20have%20such%20a%20long-term%20objective.%20You%20know%20the%20emergency%2C%20as%20we%20show%20in%20our%20book%20with%20Pratinav%20Anil%2C%20was%20a%20damage%20control%20exercise%2C%20and%20it%20could%20last%20only%20for%2022%20months%20for%20that%20very%20reason.%20Here%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20different%20game%2C%20this%20personality%20has%20an%20ideology%20and%20an%20ultimate%20goal%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Let%20me%20ask%20you%20a%20little%20about%20Nehru%2C%20Modi%20is%20constantly%20targeting%20and%20belittling%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%3B%20do%20you%20suspect%20he%20has%20a%20complex%20about%20him%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20I%20think%20so%2C%20no%20Nehru%20was%20definitely%20a%20sophisticated%20man%20who%20interacted%20freely%20with%20all%20kinds%20of%20people%2C%20he%20was%20a%20statesman%20with%20a%20vision.%20He%20had%20travelled%20to%20Europe%20when%20he%20was%20very%20young%2C%20he%20had%20an%20encyclopaedic%20culture%20as%20evident%20from%20the%20letters%20he%20wrote%20from%20jail%20%E2%80%93%20where%20he%20spent%20more%20than%20nine%20years%2C%20by%20the%20way%20%E2%80%93%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20Modi%20lacked%20this%20exposure%20to%20the%20world%2C%20he%20lacked%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20culture%2C%20his%20sense%20of%20humour%3B%20insecure%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20sense%20of%20humour%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%20of%20course%2C%20Nehru%20defined%20the%20Indian%20civilization%20as%20made%20of%20different%20religions%2C%20different%20languages.%20Modi%20believes%20that%20Hindus%20embody%20the%20Indian%20Nation%2C%20well%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20only%20one%20in%20believing%20that%3B%20this%20is%20exactly%20the%20Hindutva%20ideology%2C%20and%20Hindi%20must%20prevail.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%20federalism%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20not%20mentioned%20federalism%20yet%20but%20we%20must%20because%20as%20I%E2%80%99ve%20said%2C%20Nehru%20agreed%20finally%20to%20make%20India%20more%20federal%20by%20re-delimiting%20the%20Indian%20states%20according%20to%20the%20linguistic%20criteria%2C%20that%20was%20a%20major%20reform.%20Today%20federalism%20has%20been%20badly%20affected%20by%20centralization%20of%20power%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20only%20because%20of%20the%20tax%20processes%2C%20or%20the%20fact%20that%20neither%20the%20lockdown%2C%20nor%20demonetization%2C%20was%20discussed%20with%20Chief%20ministers.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20because%20there%20is%20an%20attempt%20at%20making%20Hindi%20more%20dominant%20as%20a%20language%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20something%20many%20states%20would%20resist%20forcefully.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20You%20know%20on%20that%20particular%20subject%20of%20federalism%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20non-BJP%20states%20that%20are%20at%20odds%20with%20Modi%2C%20but%20even%20BJP%20ruled%20states%20are%20slowly%20and%20steadily%20losing%20their%20power%20vis-a-vis%20the%20centre.%20But%20are%20you%20most%20particularly%20worried%20about%20the%20north-south%20divide%20that%20in%20a%20sense%20straddles%20the%20federalism%20issue.%20All%20the%20states%20of%20South%20India%20are%20non-BJP%20ruled%2C%20the%20states%20of%20Northern%20India%20are%20largely%20BJP%20rule%2C%20and%20the%20differences%20that%20are%20emerging%20between%20them%20in%20terms%20of%20resource%20sharing%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20Hindi%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20interference%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20and%20then%20the%20threat%20of%20deliberation.%20Are%20you%20worried%20that%20a%20fracture%20could%20open%20up%20literally%20half%20across%20India%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-w