that%20does%20not%20exist.%20So%20when%20you%20live%20in%20this%20fantasy%2C%20when%20you%20have%20painted%20such%20a%20rosy%20picture%2C%20any%20way%20questioning%20this%20myth%20opens%20a%20kind%20of%20vacuum.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20know%20the%20economy%20is%20not%20doing%20well%2C%20the%20country%20is%20terribly%20vulnerable%20vis-a-vis%20China%3B%20you%20look%20the%20other%20way%20when%20this%20question%20is%20mentioned%2C%20how%20do%20you%20admit%20that%20China%20is%20encroaching%20on%20your%20territory%20and%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20react%3F%20So%20you%20better%20not%20have%20a%20question%20on%20that%20either.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20he%20does%20with%20his%20%E2%80%98Mann%20Ki%20Baat%E2%80%99%20every%20month%2C%20painting%20a%20rosy%20picture%2C%20an%20ideal%20picture%2C%20and%20if%20he%20meets%20a%20journalist%20asking%20art%20questions%2C%20he%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20the%20same.%20You%20know%20it%20can%20only%20be%20a%20one-way%20traffic%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20an%20interaction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20This%20is%20self-%20protection%2C%20he%20can%E2%80%99t%20answer%20so%20why%20take%20questions%20at%20all%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Yeah%20and%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20respond%20to%20China%2C%20so%20why%2C%C2%A0%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20admit%20that%20there%20is%20anything%20wrong%20in%20the%20Himalayas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Before%20we%20end%20Professor%20Jaffrelot%2C%20let%20me%20ask%20you%20one%20or%20two%20questions%2C%20questions%20about%20how%20you%20think%20India%20may%20have%20changed%20as%20a%20country%2C%20as%20people%2C%20under%20Narendra%20Modi%3F%20When%20I%20was%20young%20no%20one%20accused%20Muslims%20of%20love%20jihad%20or%20cow%20lynching%2C%20no%20one%20called%20them%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBabar%20ki%20aulad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%