%20demolition%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20the%20building%20of%20the%20new%20temple%2C%20do%20it%20they%20do%20the%20job.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20common%20ground%2C%20but%20if%20you%20disaggregate%20the%2037%25%20further%20you%20certainly%20realise%20that%20upper%20caste%20middle%20class%20people%20have%20found%20in%20Modi%20the%20man%20who%20helps%20them%20to%20retain%20domination%2C%20to%20retain%20power.%20I%20repeat%20National%20populism%20is%20the%20antidote%20to%20quota%20politics%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20RSS%20wanted%20for%20sure%2C%20as%20early%20as%201990%20when%20Mandal%20occurred%2C%20when%20they%20feared%20what%20they%20called%20the%20Shudra%20revolution%2C%20and%20that%20was%20one%20of%20the%20titles%20of%20one%20of%20the%20articles%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EOrganiser%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20mouthpiece%20of%20RSS.%20The%20Shudra%20revolution%20initiated%20by%20V.P.%20Singh%2C%20that%20was%20what%20they%20wanted%20to%20stop%2C%20and%20Hindu%20naturism%20did%20the%20job.%20Now%20the%20main%20question%20for%20me%20is%20why%20do%20OBCs%2C%20and%20Dalits%20support%20Modi%20as%20well%3F%20The%20identity%20self-esteem%20question%20I%20referred%20to%20is%20certainly%20one%20factor%2C%20but%20I%20think%20there%20are%20other%20reasons%3B%20one%20is%20there%20is%20such%20a%20resentment%20vis-a-vis%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%2C%20among%20small%20OBC%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejatis%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20there%20is%20such%20a%20resentment%20vis-a-vis%20Jadav%E2%80%99s%20among%20small%20Dalit%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejatis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20And%20BJP%20has%20been%20so%20good%20at%20corrupting%20non-dominant%20OBCs%2C%20non-dominant%20Dalits%2C%20that%20they%20have%20attracted%20these%20people.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlus%20Sanskritization%2C%20emulation%20of%20the%20upper%20caste%2C%20it%20still%20works.%20Plus%20fre