0last%20TV%20channel%2C%20mainstream%20so-called%20mainstream%20TV%20channel%2C%20to%20be%20now%20captured.%20A%20technique%20by%20the%20way%20we%20saw%20elsewhere%3B%20Orb%C3%A1n%20has%20done%20it%20in%20Hungary%20very%20systematically%2C%20so%20the%20media%20problem%2C%20the%20media%20coverage%20is%20a%20problem%2C%20and%20makes%20the%20information%20of%20the%20voter%20much%20more%20biased.%20Secondly%2C%20there%20is%20a%20resource%20problem%2C%20you%20know%20the%20kind%20of%20money%20BJP%20can%20spend%20on%20an%20election%20makes%20this%20competition%20inequal%2C%20and%20electoral%20bonds%20may%20not%20make%20any%20difference%20on%20that%20front.%20So%20yes%2C%20something%20new%20but%20more%20importantly%20a%20very%20uneven%20playing%20field%2C%20making%20it%20very%20difficult%20for%20the%20opposition%20to%20win%20till%20Modi%20is%20the%20centre%20stage.%20Everything%20will%20change%20the%20moment%20Modi%20will%20leave%20the%20scene%2C%20that%20will%20be%20the%20real%20turning%20point.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07081636%2Ffe481c05-1d3b-4606-92b8-bc40bac09c3a.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07081636%2Ffe481c05-1d3b-4606-92b8-bc40bac09c3a.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07081636%2Ffe481c05-1d3b-4606-92b8-bc40bac09c3a-300x169.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695985%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EL.K.%20Advani%20and%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20BJP%20Gujarat%20website%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Absolutely!%20He%E2%80%99s%20going%20to%20be%2074%20this%20September%2C%20presumably%20this%20would%20have%20to%20be%20his%20last%205%20year%20term%20if%20he%20wins%20when%20the%20elections%20happen.%20What%20happens%20to%20the%20BJP%20after%20Narendra%20Modi%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Well%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20difficult%20question.%20What%20I%20tend%20to%20think%20is%20RSS%20will%20try%20to%20be%20Centre%20Stage%20again%2C%20you%20know%20Modi%20is%20the%20first%20BJP%20leader%20to%20side-line%20RSS%20to%20this%20extent%2C%20and%20he%20did%20it%20already%20in%20Gujarat%3B%20he%20started%20to%20tell%20the%20pracharak%20Mr%20Manmohan%20Vaidya%2C%20that%20he%20did%20not%20need%20to%20report%20to%20him.%20That%20is%20completely%20unprecedented%2C%20and%20it%20has%20remained%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20game%3B%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20cannot%20represent%20more%20than%2C%20well%2C%20the%20man%20next%20to%20him%20in%20Ayodhya%20when%20the%20temple%20is%20inaugurated.%20They%20will%20try%20to%20initiate%20a%20process%20for%20appointing%20the%20next%20BJP%20leader%2C%20probably.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20you%20have%20already%20contenders%20in%20the%20frame%3B%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20will%20he%20win%20in%20UP%20again%3F%20Will%20they%20let%20him%20win%20in%20UP%20again%3F%20And%20of%20course%20Amit%20Shah.%20I%20think%20that%20will%20be%20an%20interesting%20transition%2C%20but%20not%20an%20easy%20one.%20You%20know%20people%20like%20Modi%20have%20no%20successor%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20difficult%20to%20succeed%20a%20man%20like%20Modi%2C%20you%20know.%20especially%20when%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20dynasty%20at%20end%2C%20Maduro%20could%20never%20replace%20Chavez%3B%20which%20is%20an%20interesting%20scenario%20by%20the%20way%2C%20because%20when%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20as%20charismatic%2C%20when%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20as%20popular%20as%20the%20man%20who%20has%20created%20this%20ecosystem%2C%20you%20may%20not%20take%20the%20risk%20of%20elections%20and%20Maduro%20preferred%20not%20to%20take%20the%20risk%20of%20Elections.%20National%20populist%20usually%20take%20the%20risk%20of%20Elections%20because%20they%20are%20pretty%20sure%20to%20win%2C%20it%20was%20not%20so%20clear%20for%20Erdogan%20but%20he%20did%2C%20it%20was%20not%20so%20clear%20for%20Netanyahu%20and%20he%20lost%2C%20but%20he%20could%20stage%20a%20comeback%2C%20same%20with%20Trump.%20They%20know%20that%20they%20remain%20popular%2C%20when%20the%20popularity%20factor%20is%20not%20there%20what%20do%20you%20do%20with%20power%3F%20This%20is%20a%20very%20key%20question%20for%20the%20next%20step.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20sound%20like%20a%20reassuring%20prospect%20for%20Indian%20democracy%2C%20it%20suggests%20that%20his%20successors%20will%20find%20ways%20of%20doing%20away%20with%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20The%20question%20will%20be%20how%20robust%20are%20the%20institutions%3F%20How%20robust%20is%20the%20judiciary%3F%20And%20this%20is%20something%20that%20may%20change%20further%2C%20but%20we%20have%20to%20scrutinise%20this%20balance%20of%20power%20first%20for%20understanding%20what%20are%20the%20terms%20of%20this%20transition.%20Because%20transition%20is%20bound%20to%20happen%2C%20in%20which%20terms%3F%20and%20how%20far%20will%20the%20opposition%20parties%20close%20ranks%2C%20realising%20that%20there%20is%20so%20much%20at%20stake%3F%20Now%20in%20each%20and%20every%20country%20I%E2%80%99ve%20listed%20so%20far%2C%20finally%2C%20all%20the%20opposition%20parties%20have%20ended%2C%20in%20Poland%2C%20in%20Israel%2C%20in%20Turkey%2C%20everywhere%2C%20after%205-10-15%20years%20opposition%20parties%20realise%20that%20if%20they%20want%20to%20win%2C%20they%20have%20to%20be%20fully%20united.%20will%20the%20opposition%20in%20India%20realise%20that%20this%20is%20an%20existential%20threat%3F%20I%20mean%20this%20is%2C%20what%2