s%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04094143%2FScreenshot-2024-03-04-at-9.40.51.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20chairwoman%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20an%20online%20commenter%20reacting%20to%20the%20alleged%20gang-rape%20and%20assault%20on%20Spanish%20tourists%20in%20Jharkhand%20has%20drawn%20outrage%20from%20across%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20popular%20travel%20vlogger%20couple%20had%20been%20travelling%20through%20the%20forests%20in%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Dumka%20when%2C%20they%20said%20in%20an%20Instagram%20post%2C%20they%20were%20attacked%20by%20a%20group%20of%20men%2C%20seven%20of%20whom%20gang-raped%20the%20woman.%20The%20man%20was%20beaten%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20attacked%20in%20the%20tent%2C%20they%20beat%20us%2C%20put%20a%20knife%20to%20my%20throat%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20going%20to%20kill%20us%2C%20and%20she%20was%20raped%20by%20seven%20men%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.laprensalatina.com%2F7-men-gang-rape-spanish-tourist-in-india-3-arrested%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20Spanish%20news%20outlet%20quoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20man%20as%20having%20stated%20in%20the%20video%20which%20he%20recorded%20from%20the%20hospital%20where%20they%20are%20undergoing%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20and%20their%20announcement%20of%20it%20led%20many%20to%20observe%20on%20social%20media%20that%20in%20various%20ways%2C%20parts%20of%20India%20were%20unsafe%20to%20travel%20through%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%2C%20writer%20David%20Josef%20Volodzko%20(%40davidvolodzko)%2C%20noted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Clevel%20of%20sexual%20aggression%E2%80%9D%20that%20he%20witnessed%20while%20living%20in%20India%20for%20several%20years%20was%20unlike%20anywhere%20else%20he%20had%20ever%20been.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdavidvolodzko%2Fstatus%2F1763979126929604918%5C%22%3EHe%20wrote%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20a%20total%20stranger%2C%20a%20British%20woman%2C%20asked%20to%20sleep%20in%20my%20bed%20and%20pretend%20to%20be%20my%20girlfriend%20on%20a%20train%20ride%20because%20a%20man%20walking%20by%20in%20the%20hall%20had%20licked%20her%20foot%20and%20she%20felt%20unsafe.%20I%20introduced%20a%20female%20friend%20to%20a%20young%20Indian%20man%20and%20instead%20of%20shaking%20her%20hand%2C%20he%20groped%20her%20breast%2C%20and%20when%20she%20became%20angry%20he%20became%20extremely%20hostile%20and%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20going%20to%20have%20to%20fight%20the%20guy.%20I%20never%20met%20a%20female%20traveler%20who%20had%20not%20been%20groped%20or%20assaulted%20or%20worse%2C%20even%20if%20they%20had%20only%20been%20in%20country%20for%20mere%20days.%20I%20love%20India.%20It%20is%20and%20always%20will%20be%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20places%20in%20the%20world.%20But%20I%20have%20advised%20female%20friends%20who%20asked%20me%20not%20to%20travel%20there%20alone.%20This%20is%20a%20real%20problem%20in%20Indian%20society%20that%20warrants%20more%20attention%20and%20that%20I%20hope%20will%20improve%20in%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20sparked%20various%20reactions%20with%20some%20agreeing%20and%20many%20launching%20attacks%20on%20Volodzko.%20Among%20the%20latter%20was%20the%20NCW%20chairwoman%20Rekha%20Sharma%2C%20who%20equated%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20safety%20of%20women%20with%20defamation%20of%20the%20country.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsharmarekha%2Fstatus%2F1764166577212313709%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3ESharma%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDid%20you%20ever%20report%20the%20incident%20to%20Police%3F%20If%20not%20than%20you%20are%20totally%20an%20irresponsible%20person.%20Writing%20only%20on%20social%20media%20and%20defaming%20whole%20country%20is%20not%20good%20choice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20Sharma%20heads%2C%20the%20NCW%2C%20is%20a%20statutory%20body%20under%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20topmost%20groups%20which%20can%20uphold%20concerns%20relevant%20to%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20body%20has%20made%20news%20for%20the%20wrong%20reasons%20of%20late.%20In%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-a-complaint-on-the-may-4-assault-was-sent-to-ncw-but-the-complainants-never-got-a-reply%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20learnt%20that%20the%20NCW%20had%20been%20sent%20on%20June%2012%20a%20complaint%20on%20a%20harrowing%20May%204%20incident%20in%20Manipur%2C%20in%20which%20two%20Kuki%20women%20were%20assaulted%20by%20a%20mob%20during%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20and%20video%20recorded.%20But%20the%20NCW%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20or%20acknowledge%20the%20complainants%2C%20the%20report%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20when%20her%20older%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faap-ncw-chairperson-rekha-sharma%5C%22%3Etweets%3C%2Fa%3E%20making%20fun%20of%20women%2C%20politicians%20and%20women%20politicians%20drew%20ire%20from%20the%20public%2C%20Sharma%20claimed%20that%20her%20Twitter%20handle%20had%20been%20hacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolodzko%2C%20in%20his%20long%20reply%20to%20Sharma%2C%20wrote%20that%20far%20from%20defaming%20India%2C%20he%20was%20attempting%20to%20point%20out%20a%20flaw%20in%20a%20country%20he%20otherwise%20%E2%80%9Cloved.%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdavidvolodzko%2Fstatus%2F1764386371815219322%5C%22%3EHe%20also%20added%20criticism%20of%20the%20NCW%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20what%20you%20get%20from%20NCW%20types.%20I%20am%20not%20Indian%2C%20so%20take%20my%20view%20for%20whatever%20it%20is%20worth%2C%20but%20my%20Indian%20friends%20do%20not%20seem%20to%20have%20much%20respect%2C%20if%20any%2C%20for%20NCW%20and%20one%20reason%20for%20this%20is%20because%20it%20has%20a%20deplorable%20habit%20of%20blaming%20women%20when%20they%20are%20attacked%2C%20raped%20or%20even%20murdered.%20NCW%20makes%20India%20less%20safe%20for%20women%20when%20it%20does%20these%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6And%20yet%20here%20she%20is%20with%20the%20gall%20to%20accuse%20me%20of%20defaming%20India.%20Ms.%20Sharma%2C%20it%20is%20you%20who%20defame%20India%20by%20presiding%20over%20a%20group%20called%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20and%20doing%20nothing%20about%20the%20issue%20noted%20above%2C%20and%20then%20criticizing%20people%20like%20me%20for%20drawing%20attention%20to%20this%20important%20matter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20others%20%E2%80%93%20mostly%20women%20%E2%80%93%20also%20noted%20that%20they%20were%20appalled%20at%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20recounting%20the%20everyday%20horrors%20of%20their%20lives%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20annual%20report%20had%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fcrime-against-women-india-4-ncrb-report-2023%5C%22%3Estaggering%20number%20of%20cases%20of%20violence%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%20was%20the%20equivalent%20of%2051%20FIRs%20every%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20was%20going%20to%20completely%20avoid%20this%20but%20since%20this%20is%20all%20over%20my%20TL%20%E2%80%94%20India%20is%20extremely%20unsafe%20for%20women.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20a%20SINGLE%20woman%20who%20has%20not%20faced%20some%20form%20of%20harassment%20or%20worse%20while%20in%20India.%20Really%20vile%20to%20say%20that%20women%20are%20baselessly%20shaming%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Sohni%20Chakrabarti%20(%40sohni_c)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsohni_c%2Fstatus%2F1764336050514559114%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5C