20in%20public%20meetings%20at%20Aurangabad%20and%20Begusarai%20that%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20was%20%E2%80%9Cshy%20of%20talking%20about%20what%20his%20father%20%5BLalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%5D%20had%20done.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20he%20not%20talking%20about%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20had%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20often%20labels%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20%E2%80%98jungle%20raaj%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20appeared%20to%20directly%20address%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20he%20is%20silent%20on%20his%20father%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CModi%20ji%2C%20please%20keep%20your%20ears%20open%20and%20glasses%20clean%20to%20hear%20and%20see%20me%20clearly.%20My%20father%20liberated%20millions%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20marginalised%20people%20from%20the%20bondage%20of%20slavery%2C%20he%20gave%20them%20voice%20and%20liberty.%20The%20Railways%20earned%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%2090%2C000%20crores%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20the%20Railway%20minister.%20He%20got%20wheels%20and%20wagon%20factories%20opened%20in%20Bihar.%20He%20regularised%20the%20services%20of%20coolies%20and%20introduced%20earthen%20cups%20for%20tea%20in%20the%20trains%20to%20give%20employment%20to%20potters.%20What%20have%20the%20Railways%20done%20under%20your%20rule%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%20has%20launched%20this%20frontal%20attack%20on%20the%20PM%20at%20a%20time%20when%20many%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20believed%20be%20haunted%20by%20the%20fear%20of%20central%20investigating%20agencies%20charging%20them%20in%20corruption%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2F10-day-yatra-and-a-mega-rally-tejashwi-attempts-to-go-beyond-muslim-yadav-formula%5C%22%3E10-Day%20Yatra%20and%20a%20Mega%20Rally%3A%20Tejashwi%20Attempts%20to%20Go%20Beyond%20Muslim-Yadav%20Formula%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20has%20fought%20them%20(Sangh%20Parivar)%2C%20braving%20all%20the%20tortures%20and%20tribulations.%20Rahul%20ji%20and%20Akhilesh%20ji%20have%20got%20notices%20from%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%20I%20am%20among%20several%20of%20my%20family%20members%20facing%20the%20investigating%20agencies%E2%80%99%20heat.%20But%20mark%20my%20words%2C%20I%20will%20fight%E2%80%A6I%20won%E2%80%99t%20bow%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tejashwi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20present%20in%20the%20rally%20were%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20Left%20parties%E2%80%99%20leaders%2C%20Dipankar%20Bhattacharya%2C%20D.%20Raja%20and%20Sitaram%20Yechury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CSome%20people%20describe%20your%20BJP%20as%20a%20washing%20machine%20where%20the%20people%20go%20to%20get%20laundered.%20But%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20really%20a%20washing%20machine%2C%20it%20is%20a%20dustbin%20to%20hold%20the%20garbage%20discarded%20by%20all%20other%20parties.%20Against%20this%20garbage%20party%2C%20is%20my%20RJD%20%E2%80%93%20an%20abbreviation%20of%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98rights%2C%20jobs%20and%20development%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%E2%80%99s%20rallies%20were%20attended%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20chief%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20his%20new%20deputy%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20Samrat%20Choudhary%2C%20among%20others.%20They%20were%2C%20of%20course%2C%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Mahagathbandhan%20%3Cem%3Eka%3C%2Fem%3E%20Jan%20Vishwas%20rally%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20the%20grand%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20rally%20for%20public%20faith%20%E2%80%93%20saw%20enormous%20response.%20The%20Gandhi%20Maidan%20was%20a%20sea%20of%20humanity%20with%20people%20jostling%20with%20each%20other%20and%20spilling%20over%20into%20the%20streets%20in%20the%20city%20despite%20the%20intermittent%20drizzle%20and%20cold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FJzktUiRDcp0%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A7%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%A6%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%B5%20%7C%20The%20Wire%20Live%20%7C%20Patna%20%7C%20Gandhi%20Maidan%20%7C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20%7C%20RJD%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJobs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20training%20his%20guns%20on%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20Tejashwi%20appeared%20to%20keep%20the%20jobs%20question%20front%20and%20centre%20and%20tried%20to%20present%20himself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98store%20house%E2%80%99%20of%20employment.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20same%20Gandhi%20Maidan%20in%20which%20I%20made%20a%20reluctant%20CM%20%5Ba%20jab%20at%20Nitish%20Kumar%20who%20left%20the%20alliance%20recently%5D%20distribute%20over%20two%20lakh%20appointment%20letters.%20Do%20you%20remember%20it%20or%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%20Tejashwi%20asked.%20People%20responded%20with%20rousing%20cries%20of%20%E2%80%98Tejashwi%20%3Cem%3Ezindabad%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployment%20has%20been%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20ever%20since%20the%202020%20elections.%20Behind%20his%20description%20of%20Modi%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfactory%20of%20lies%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20had%20reneged%20on%20his%20promise%20to%20give%20two%20crores%20of%20jobs%20annually%20apart%20from%20raising%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20for%20agricultural%20products%20up%20to%2050%25%20and%20doubling%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20by%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20Modi%20ji%20who%20failed%20on%20several%20of%20his%20guarantees%20in%20the%20past%20is%20talking%20about%20%E2%80%98Modi%20%3Cem%3Eki%3C%2Fem%3E%20guarantee%E2%80%99.%20What%20guarantee%20he%20is%20talking%20about%3F%E2%80%9D%20Tejashwi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWill%20he%20%5BModi%5D%20guarantee%20the%20stay%20of%20my%20uncle%20%5BTejashwi%20calls%20Nitish%20%E2%80%98uncle%E2%80%99%5D%20with%20him%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Tejashwi%20has%20tried%20to%20match%20the%20gift%20of%20rhetoric%20that%20his%20father%20had%2C%20it%20is%20too%20early%20to%20say%20if%20he%20will%20prove%20to%20have%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20exact%20power%20to%20mesmerise%20the%20masses%20and%20take%20on%20political%20opponents%20in%20the%20parliament%20and%20on%20the%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frjds-jan-vishwas-patna-rally-turns-into-a-big-india-push-first-in-hindi-belt-in-2024%5C%22%3ERJD%E2%80%99s%20Jan%20Vishwas%20Patna%20Rally%20Turns%20Into%20a%20Big%20INDIA%20Push%2C%20First%20in%20Hindi%20Belt%20in%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoft%20on%20Nitish%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%20to%20his%20barbs%20against%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Tejashwi%20was%20mild%20on%20Nitish.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20uncle%20deserted%20us.%20But%20I%20have%20no%20issue%3B%20I%20respected%20him%3B%20I%20will%20keep%20on%20respecting%20him.%20He%20is%20an%20old%20man.%20I%20have%20all%20regards%20for%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20point%2C%20though%2C%20he%20was%20unsparing.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20remember%20who%20talked%20about%20jobs%20and%20employment%20first.%20It%20was%20I%20who%20promised%20to%20give%2010%20lakh%20jobs%20during%20my%202020%20election%20campaigns.%20But%2C%20Nitish%20screamed%20at%20me%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98Where%20will%20we%20get%20the%20money%20from%3F%20Will%20I%20bring%20it%20from%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20house%3F%20This%20is%20impossible%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%2C%20who%20was%20driven%20to%20the%20opposition%20after%20Nitish%20switched%20sides%20to%20the%20BJP%20on%20January%2028%2C%20claimed%20that%20this%20is%20what%20Nitish%20had%20said%20when%20reacting%20to%20his%20promise%20of%2010%20lakh%20jobs%20in%202020.%20But%20within%20a%20week%20of%20joining%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20in%20August%202022%2C%20Nitish%20in%20his%20Independence%20Day%20address%20on%20August%2015%20at%20the%20same%20Gandhi%20Maidan%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20fulfil%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20promise%20of%20about%2010%20lakh%20jobs.%20The%20alliance%20government%20handed%20out%20about%204.5%20lakh%20jobs%20during%2017%20months%20of%20its%20tenure%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%20is%20clearly%20keen%20to%20make%20employment%20the%20central%20issue%20of%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202024%20elections%20campaigns%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20same%20manner%20in%20which%20he%20did%20in%202020.%20In%20between%20the%20proceedings%2C%20the%20RJD%20spokesman%20and%20MP%20(Rajya%20Sabha)%2C%20Manoj%20Jha%20raised%20the%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ENaukri%20matlab%3C%2Fem%3E%20Tejaswhi%20Yadav%20(Tejashwi%20means%20jobs)%E2%80%9D%20which%20the%20crowd%20responded%20to%20with%20excitement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709522498000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04085042%2FGHmG5r9XUAAVpLz.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftejashwi-yadav-jan-vishwas-rally-modi-nitish%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tejashwi%20launched%20a%20frontal%20attack%20on%20the%20PM%20at%20a%20time%20when%20many%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20believ