ring%20students%20at%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20BML%20Munjal%20University%20(BMU)%2C%20were%20developing%20an%20electric%20racing%20car%20for%20a%20competition%20organised%20by%20Baja%20SAE%20(Society%20of%20Automotive%20Engineers)%20India%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-profit%20engineering%20and%20scientific%20society%20dedicated%20to%20the%20mobility%20community%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20competition%20where%20college%20students%20design%20and%20develop%20vehicles%20and%20compete%20on%20automobile%20racing%20circuits%20like%20the%20Buddh%20International%20Circuit.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20good%20programme%20for%20budding%20engineers%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Utkarsh%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20component%20of%20developing%20an%20electric%20racing%20car%20was%20installing%20a%20lithium-ion%20(Li-ion)%20battery.%20However%2C%20finding%20such%20a%20battery%20in%202017%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy%20because%2C%20back%20then%2C%20nobody%20in%20India%20was%20manufacturing%20it%20on%20a%20significant%20scale.%20But%20they%20eventually%20found%20a%20company%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329424%2Fludhiana-woman-grows-200-plants-in-terrace-garden-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELudhiana%2C%20Punjab%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20importing%20batteries%20and%20distributing%20them%20all%20over%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20students%2C%20we%20approached%20that%20company%20for%20a%20battery%20and%20they%20even%20agreed%20to%20give%20us%20one%20for%20this%20project.%20But%20for%20six%20months%20they%20kept%20delaying%20the%20delivery%20of%20this%20battery%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20participate%20in%20the%20competition.%20Frustrated%20by%20this%20outcome%2C%20Vikrant%20and%20I%20began%20discussing%20why%20these%20Li-ion%20batteries%20aren%E2%80%99t%20being%20made%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20in%20these%20batteries%20you%20have%20Li-ion%20cells%20and%20these%20aren%E2%80%99t%20manufactured%20in%20India%20for%20the%20very%20simple%20reason%20that%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20find%20the%20raw%20materials%2C%20i.e.%20lithium%2C%20cobalt%20and%20nickel%2C%20required%20to%20make%20them.%20Also%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300789%2Fretrofitting-how-to-convert-your-old-cars-into-electric-vehicles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20vehicle%3C%2Fa%3E%20(EV)%20consumption%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20too%20heavy%20and%20no%20one%20realised%20that%20this%20sector%20would%20take%20off%20soon.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20whatever%20OEMs%20(original%20equipment%20manufacturers)%20in%20India%20needed%2C%20they%20were%20importing%20those%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20their%20college%20semester%20project%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20build%20Li-ion%20cells%20at%20a%20Rs%20200%20crore%20R%26amp%3BD%20laboratory%20set%20up%20on%20campus.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20ordered%20lithium%20and%20cobalt%20from%20China.%20Due%20to%20various%20reasons%2C%20these%20materials%20didn%E2%80%99t%20arrive%20on%20time%20for%20our%20project.%20To%20complete%20it%2C%20we%20bought%20some%20old%20Li-ion%20cells%20from%20the%20market%2C%20extracted%20whatever%20materials%20we%20could%20in%20very%20impure%20forms%20and%20then%20fabricated%20Li-ion%20cells%20(half%20cells)%20that%20delivered%20some%20energy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20acquire%20these%20materials%20in%20India%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20start%20recycling%20old%20Li-ion%20batteries.%20We%20predicted%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20Li-ion%20batteries%20are%20going%20to%20enter%20the%20country%2C%20and%20if%20we%20recycle%20them%2C%20these%20materials%20can%20be%20reused%20