y%20a%20major%20Lithium-ion%20battery%20recycling%20startup%20which%20produces%20battery-grade%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20their%20core%20objectives%20is%20to%20create%20a%20domestic%20circular%20supply%20chain%20of%20materials%20like%20lithium%2C%20nickel%20and%20cobalt%2C%20among%20others%2C%20and%20lessen%20the%20requirement%20for%20mining%20them.%20The%20company%20extracts%20rare%20earth%20metals%2C%20such%20as%20lithium%2C%20cobalt%2C%20nickel%20and%20manganese%20from%20used%20Li-ion%20cells%2C%20which%20are%20then%20bought%20by%20a%20variety%20of%20industries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20EVs%2C%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20electroplating%20and%20fertiliser.%20But%20if%20these%20used%20cells%20have%20some%20charge%20left%2C%20they%20repurpose%20them%20into%20batteries%20for%20off-grid%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F256764%2Fmumbai-startup-electric-vehicle-features-charger-cost-install-magenta-street-light-ev-charging-solutions-solar-energy-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20EV%20chargers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20inverters%2C%20or%20other%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20developed%20an%20innovative%20procedure%20for%20recycling%20various%20batteries%2C%20employing%20specialised%20techniques%20and%20advanced%20hydrometallurgical%20processes.%20As%20a%20major%20supplier%20of%20sustainable%20battery%20solutions%20in%20India%2C%20they%20have%20even%20secured%20a%20patent%20for%20their%20Zero%20Waste-Zero%20Emission%20Technology%20and%20successfully%20recycled%20about%20220%20million%20batteries%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201137px)%20100vw%2C%201137px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-2-1709299204.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221137%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Recycling%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%20is%20good%20