0and%20the%20sales%20of%20the%20suitcase%20have%20been%20the%20highest%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20company%20has%20been%20experiencing%20more%20demand%20from%20the%20Southern%20part%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20product%20delivers%20what%20it%20claims.%20You%20know%20how%20you%20keep%20losing%20your%20wallet%20here%20and%20there.%20The%20problem%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20issue%20for%20me%20because%20I%20can%20easily%20track%20it%20with%20my%20phone.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20the%20charging%20facility%20so%20I%20do%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20my%20phone%20dying%20as%20I%20can%20charge%20it%20on%20the%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aqib%2C%20a%20customer%20who%20purchased%20their%20smart%20wallet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20duo%20went%20on%20to%20Shark%20Tank%20and%20charmed%20all%20the%20sharks.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20at%20the%20show%2C%20our%20luggage%20was%20the%20star%20of%20the%20evening.%20All%20the%20sharks%20loved%20riding%20on%20it%20and%20they%20kept%20moving%20it%20around%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20happily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20their%20experience%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20experience%20was%20amazing.%20Before%20entering%2C%20we%20were%20very%20nervous%20and%20my%20hands%20were%20sweating%20but%20once%20we%20started%20talking%2C%20all%20my%20anxieties%20went%20away.%20Although%20the%20sharks%20had%20a%20few%20doubts%20about%20the%20market%20of%20the%20products%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20convince%20them.%20We%20went%20inside%20to%20crack%20a%20deal%20and%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20we%20could%20do%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-5-1709213260.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20were%20able%20to%