0kind%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarah%20had%20also%20grown%20up%20with%20dogs%20and%20other%20pets.%20She%20had%20keenly%20watched%20her%20mother%2C%20aunt%20and%20grandmother%20feed%20them%2C%20groom%20them%20and%20love%20them%20like%20their%20own%20family%20members.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Sarah%20had%20no%20fear%20of%20dogs%20and%20nurtured%20a%20strong%20affection%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20always%20saw%20them%20showing%20kindness%20to%20animals.%20They%20never%20explicitly%20instructed%20me%20to%20be%20kind%20to%20animals.%20It%E2%80%99s%20just%20something%20I%20imbibed%20by%20watching%20them.%20Eventually%2C%20there%20came%20a%20time%20when%20my%20mother%20would%20tell%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98Guddi%2C%20you%20must%20start%20a%20shelter%E2%80%99.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338562%2Fmumbai-police-cid-first-quadruple-murder-case-indian-sherlock-holmes-vaidyanath-sami%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20Mumbai%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20more%20concerned%20with%20raising%20my%20daughter.%20However%2C%20my%20mother%20would%20keep%20insisting%20that%20I%20should%20start%20an%20animal%20shelter%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Sarah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20moved%20to%20Chennai%20and%20got%20PK%20home%2C%20my%20mother%20was%20very%20happy.%20Also%2C%20since%20I%20had%20more%20time%20for%20myself%20after%20moving%20to%20Chennai%2C%20I%20told%20my%20mother%20that%20I%20would%20think%20about%20opening%20a%20dog%20shelter.%20In%202016%2C%20however%2C%20my%20mother%20suddenly%20passed%20away.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20my%20aunt%20also%20passed%20away%20within%20a%20year%20of%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22