0the%20inner%20ear%20or%20cochlea%20to%20provide%20sound%20signals%20to%20the%20brain%20by%20stimulating%20the%20inner%20ear%2C%20which%20helps%20the%20child%20to%20start%20hearing.%20There%20is%20an%20internal%20and%20external%20device%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implant%20comprises%20an%20external%20component%20placed%20behind%20the%20ear%20and%20a%20second%20component%20surgically%20implanted%20under%20the%20skin.%20This%20surgery%20can%20be%20performed%20as%20early%20as%20six%20to%20eight%20months%20of%20age%20and%20ideally%20should%20be%20completed%20by%20the%20time%20the%20child%20reaches%20three%20years%20old%2C%20ensuring%20timely%20access%20to%20schooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20newborn%20hearing%20screening%2C%20the%20doctors%20can%20assess%20if%20the%20baby%20has%20any%20hearing%20loss.%20Through%20a%20battery%20of%20tests%20and%20follow-ups%2C%20by%20the%20time%20the%20child%20is%20three%20to%20four%20months%20old%2C%20it%20becomes%20clear%20if%20the%20baby%20needs%20a%20cochlear%20implant%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20baby%20reaches%20eight%20months%20old%2C%20they%20are%20ready%20for%20the%20surgery%2C%20which%20typically%20lasts%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%20However%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20surgery%20alone%20addresses%20only%2020%20percent%20of%20the%20problem.%20What%E2%80%99s%20equally%20important%20is%20the%20post-surgery%20Auditory%20Verbal%20Therapy%20(AVT)%2C%20which%20spans%20two%20years%20and%20requires%20parental%20involvement%20to%20ensure%20the%20child%20develops%20spoken%20language%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETHF%20states%20that%20each%20cochlear%20implant%20procedure%20with%20the%20device%2C%20surgery%20and%20rehabilitation%20costs%20about%20Rs%208-9%20lakh%20per%20ear.%20THF%20also%20provides%20support%20for%20this%20therapy%20and%20ensures%20that%20parents%20from%20underprivileged%20backgrounds%20have%20access%20to%20therapists%20and%20can%20continue%20the%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20ignore%20warning%20signs%20of%20hearing%20loss%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cochlear%20implant%20surgery%20is%20most%20effective%20when%20done%20in%20the%200-5%20age%20group%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343118%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECochlear%20implant%20surgery%20is%20most%20effective%20when%20done%20in%20the%200-3%20age%20group%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20in%20Sukhjot%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20many%20parents%20come%20to%20doctors%20late%2C%20says%20Dr%20Bhatia.%20This%20lack%20of%20awareness%20causes%20significant%20delays%20in%20the%20surgery%2C%20affecting%20outcomes.%20An%20internal%20study%20conducted%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20revealed%20that%20hearing%20outcomes%20among%20children%20who%20received%20implants%20between%20the%20ages%20of%20zero%20and%20three%20were%20two%20and%20a%20half%20times%20improved