void%20ear%20injuries%20and%20promptly%20seek%20medical%20attention%20in%20case%20of%20infections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20a%20decade%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20programme%2C%20the%20Foundation%20has%20observed%20that%20the%20success%20of%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20is%20based%20on%20a%20multitude%20of%20factors.%20The%20cause%20and%20type%20of%20hearing%20impairment%20have%20an%20effect%2C%20but%20so%20does%20the%20age%20of%20the%20child%2C%20time%20elapsed%20since%20the%20onset%20of%20hearing%20loss%2C%20active%20implant%20use%2C%20and%20also%20family%20support%20which%20affects%20the%20quality%20of%20speech%20and%20educational%20rehabilitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Bhatia%20urges%20parents%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20ignore%20any%20warning%20signs%20or%20doubts.%20Just%20go%20and%20consult%20a%20doctor.%20Cochlear%20implants%20are%20nothing%20to%20be%20wary%20of%20%E2%80%93%20they%20are%20a%20well%20established%20technology%20and%20can%20change%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20life%20for%20the%20better%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20The%20Hans%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708836709000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-scaled.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343108%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20spotting%20hearing%20loss%20in%20children%20early%20on%20and%20offering%20life-changing%20surgery%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20has%20helped%20over%20900%20children%20with%20its%20Cochlear%20Implant%20Programme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A63%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343108%2Fthe-hans-foundation-cochlear-implant-program-for-children-with-hearing-loss-deaf-speech-hospital-surgery%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20To